Package com.fssa.freshnest.constants

Class StillConstants

java.lang.Object
com.fssa.freshnest.constants.StillConstants
public class StillConstants extends Object
This class contains constant messages related to still (possibly an image or media content) validation, creation, update, deletion, and other still-related operations.
Author:
SusikumarPitchaimuth
